{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881587594,"sessionID":"ses_28535df40ffe95VE8PKIYkSDM5","part":{"id":"prt_d7aca8769001uYvwJUs3GnWRfY","messageID":"msg_d7aca7449001qspLSxrm8ZcnRz","sessionID":"ses_28535df40ffe95VE8PKIYkSDM5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b4208be1cf8c4bbcaa0a9ac0fbc7609e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient |\n8: | Module | `sdk-python` |\n9: | Language | Python |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient Implementation (ST-1)\n18: \n19: - [ ] **T1.1**: Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.__init__` with router_url, namespace, agent_name, timeout, connect_timeout\n20:   - Purpose: Initialize HTTP client for Router data plane communication\n21:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n22:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestDataPlaneClientInit -v`\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T1.2**: Implement `SESSION_HEADER` class constant `\"x-agentcube-session-id\"`\n25:   - Purpose: Define session header name as class-level constant\n26:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n27:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.clients.agent_runtime_data_plane import AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient; print(AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER)\"`\n28: \n29: - [ ] **T1.3**: Implement base_url construction via `urljoin`\n30:   - Purpose: Build base_url as `/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n31:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n32:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestBaseURLConstruction -v`\n33: \n34: - [ ] **T1.4**: Implement HTTP session with connection pooling (pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)\n35:   - Purpose: Create requests.Session with HTTPAdapter for connection pooling\n36:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n37:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestConnectionPooling -v`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T1.5**: Implement `bootstrap_session_id()` method\n40:   - Purpose: GET base_url to bootstrap session, extract session_id from `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n41:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n42:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestBootstrapSessionID -v`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T1.6**: Implement `bootstrap_session_id()` missing header handling\n45:   - Purpose: Raise ValueError when `x-agentcube-session-id` header missing in response\n46:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n47:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestBootstrapSessionID::test_bootstrap_missing_header -v`\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T1.7**: Implement `invoke()` method with session_id and payload parameters\n50:   - Purpose: POST to base_url with json=payload and session header\n51:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n52:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestInvoke -v`\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T1.8**: Implement `invoke()` headers with `x-agentcube-session-id` and `Content-Type: application/json`\n55:   - Purpose: Set both session header and Content-Type on POST requests\n56:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n57:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/te